items.zh: 最大屏幕抖动来源数量

Toggles the Slabfish hat's backpack. Available to Tier 3+ patrons.
Toggles the Slabfish hat's type. Available to Tier 4+ patrons.

items.zh: 有概率躲避弹射物伤害

items.en: This is not a Falconry Glove
This is not a Falconry Glove
Increases the height of Straddleboard jumps.
Gives the rider of the Straddleboard Fire Resistance.
Makes Bone Serpents neutral towards the rider of the Straddleboard.
items.zh: 当跨板手骑着跨板时可以令骨蟒保持中立。

items.en: Straddleboard returns instantly to the rider's inventory when broken.
items.zh: 当跨板损坏时，会自动收入跨板手的物品栏。

items.en: Discover the unique creatures of the world
items.zh: 发现世上独一无二的生物

items.en: Craft a Crimson Mosquito Larvae from a maggot and a special proboscis
items.zh: 用一条蛆和一个特殊的口器来合成绯红蚊子幼虫

items.en: Craft a Blood Sprayer from the drops of a Crimson Mosquito
items.zh: 用绯红蚊子的掉落物来合成一个血液喷雾器

items.en: Tame a Warped Toad, the perfect defense against any giant bug, with some larvae
items.zh: 用一些幼虫来驯服一只对于任何巨型昆虫都具有完美防御的诡异蟾蜍
用花儿来繁殖两只蜂鸟

items.en: Craft a Hummingbird Feeder in order to keep hummingbirds nearby
items.zh: 合成一个可以吸引蜂鸟们的蜂鸟喂食器
一 个 野 餐 篮

items.en: Tame a Grizzly Bear by feeding it honey and salmon
items.zh: 用蜂蜜和鲑鱼来喂食灰熊并驯服它

items.en: Craft a Maraca with a Rattlesnake rattle
items.zh: 用响尾蛇的响尾来合成一个沙槌

items.en: Give a Maraca to a cockroach and enjoy the show. ¡La Cucaracha!
items.zh: 把一个沙槌丢给蟑螂，然后享受表演吧！¡La Cucaracha!

items.en: Tame a capuchin monkey with bananas
items.zh: 用香蕉驯服一只卷尾猴

items.en: Receive a blessing from the great and noble sunbird
items.zh: 接受来自崇高无上的太阳鸟的祝福

items.en: Craft sopa de macaco with a banana peel
items.zh: 用一块香蕉皮来合成一碗猴儿汤

items.en: Craft a crocodile chestplate from many crocodile scutes
items.zh: 用许多片鳄鱼鳞甲来合成一件鳄鱼鳞甲胸甲

items.en: Tame a Mantis Shrimp with many feedings of Tropical Fish
items.zh: 用许多热带鱼来喂食皮皮虾并驯服它

items.en: Breed two crocodiles with rotten flesh. Careful not to trample their eggs!
items.zh: 给两只鳄鱼喂食腐肉，注意别踩碎了它们的蛋！
龟 假 鳄 威

items.en: Shear a moss-covered Alligator Snapping Turtle and obtain a Spiked Scute
items.zh: 修剪一只披满苔藓的大鳄龟并得到一个锥形鳞甲

items.en: Sneak and give a tamed Mantis Shrimp a bucket of water so that it can live on land indefinitely
items.zh: 偷偷给一只被驯服过的皮皮虾一桶水，这样它就可以一直生活在陆地上了

items.en: Be granted a blessing from a wild Orca
items.zh: 得到来自野生虎鲸的祝福

items.en: Obtain an Acacia Blossom from breaking Acacia Leaves
items.zh: 打碎金合欢树叶并得到一朵金合欢花

items.en: Tame an elephant by feeding it Acacia Blossoms
items.zh: 用金合欢花来喂食大象并驯服它
陆地上最大的哺乳动物

items.en: Tame a tusked elephant when it is a baby
items.zh: 驯服一只处于婴儿时期的大象

items.en: Place a colored carpet on an elephant
items.zh: 把带有颜色的地毯放在大象身上

items.en: Encounter a Soul Vulture in the nether
items.zh: 在下界遇见一只灵魂鹫

items.en: Obtain a soul heart from slaying a bloated Soul Vulture
items.zh: 通过杀死一只灵魂鹫来获得一个灵魂之心

items.en: Lure a Spectre in the end with a Soul Heart. Use a lead on them to hitch a ride!
items.zh: 在末地用灵魂之心引诱一只灵翼。并用一根拴绳给拴起来！

items.en: Encounter a Guster during a stormy day in the desert
items.zh: 当沙漠里刮起沙尘暴时遇到一只沙风怪

items.en: Craft a Gustmaker. Now you can make your own mini-storms!
items.zh: 合成一个造风器。现在你可以制作一个属于你自己的小型风暴了！

items.en: Craft a Pocket Of Sand. Sha-sha!
items.zh: 合成一个含沙射之袋。唦唦！

items.en: Feed a Crimson Mosquito a strange, fungal creature covered in Warped Fungus. Watch as the Crimson Mosquito transforms!
items.zh: 给绯红蚊子喂食一种覆盖着诡异菌的真菌生物。然后看着绯红蚊子进行转变吧！

items.en: Slay the Warped Mosco, the swole defender of the Warped Forest.
items.zh: 杀死诡异蚊鬼，诡异森林里强壮的保卫者。

items.en: Craft a Hemolyph Blaster, the ultimate upgrade to the Blood Sprayer.
items.zh: 合成一个血淋巴喷射器，血液喷射器的最终版本。

items.en: Encounter a Straddler in the Basalt Deltas.
items.zh: 在玄武岩三角洲中遇到一只跨座兽。

items.en: Feed a Stradpole some Mosquito Larva, in hopes of turning it into a Straddler.
items.zh: 给跨座蝌蚪喂食一些蚊子幼虫，希望能把它变成跨座兽。

items.en: Craft a Straddleboard from some Netherite and Straddlerite.
items.zh: 用一些下界合金和跨座晶石来合成一个跨板。
遇见一只鸸鹋。请谨慎行事。

items.en: See an emu dodge a launched projectile.
items.zh: 看到过一只鸸鹋躲避发射出的弹射物
我们实施了一次小型的拖捕行动......

items.en: Save a beached Cachalot Whale by pushing it into the water, and then have it reward you by coughing up some Ambergris
items.zh: 把一头搁浅的抹香鲸推入水中, 然后它会吐出一些龙涎香作为回报

items.en: Craft an Echolocator, which can reveal nearby caves
items.zh: 合成一个可以寻找附近洞穴的回声定位器

items.en: Craft an Endolocator, which can reveal nearby End Portal Frames
items.zh: 合成一个可以寻找末地门的末影定位器

items.en: Stomp on a Leafcutter Anthill - beware the angry denizens within!
items.zh: 踩在切叶蚁丘上——得当心里面愤怒的住民！

items.en: Like a Truffle, with more Ant
items.zh: 就像一块沾满了蚂蚁的松露

items.en: Harvest Gongylidia from a Leafcutter Ant Chamber underground. Place Shroomlight near the chamber to make sure you don't upset the locals
items.zh: 从地下的切叶蚁室收集菌丝球。把菌光体放在蚁室的附近来确保不会惹怒它们。

items.en: Obtain a Leafcutter Ant Pupa, which can be placed on dirt to start a Leafcutter Ant colony.
items.zh: 获得一个可以放在泥土上的切叶蚁蛹，以此来建立一个切叶蚁群。

items.en: Encounter an Enderiophage, a giant biomechanical construct found in the End Midlands. Be careful not to catch Ender Flu!
items.zh: 遇见一只末影噬菌体，发现于末地中型岛屿的一个巨大生物力学结构体。小心别传染上末影流感！

items.en: Obtain a Capsid from a slain Enderiophage. Use it to display items or to transfer them upwards
items.zh: 通过杀死末影噬菌体来获得一个衣壳。使用它来展示物品或者往上传输物品。

items.en: Catch the Ender Flu effect. Cure it by eating many Chorus Fruit or drinking milk. Be sure not to let it run its toll!
items.zh: 患上了末影流感。可以通过多吃紫颂果或者牛奶来治愈。确保别让它造成伤亡。
预备 末地 发射

items.en: Craft an Enderiophage Rocket, which can be used in place of Firework Rockets when in the End.
items.zh: 合成一个末影噬菌体火箭，它可以代替烟花火箭在末地中发射。

items.en: Tame a bald eagle with fish oil.
Craft a Falconry Glove from Leather and Hair of Bear. Use it to pick up and launch tamed eagles!
items.zh: 使用皮革和灰熊毛皮合成一双猎鹰手套。使用猎鹰手套可以与雕取得信任并驯服它！

items.en: Craft a Falconry Hood from Leather and a Roadrunner Feather. Eagles wearing one can be manually directed!
items.zh: 使用皮革和走鹃羽毛合成一顶猎鹰兜帽。可以直接给雕手动戴上它。

items.en: Kill any creature from 100 blocks away with an eagle wearing a hood.
items.zh: 让一只戴着兜帽的老鹰杀死100个方块以外的任意生物。

items.en: Receive a Tiger's Blessing after feeding it Porkchops, Chicken or other meats.
items.zh: 在给老虎喂食猪肉、鸡肉或者其他肉类以后，获得来自老虎的祝福。

items.en: Encounter a Tarantula Hawk in a desert.
items.zh: 在沙漠里遇见一只沙漠蛛蜂

items.en: Tame a Tarantula Hawk by feeding it Spider Eyes.
items.zh: 用蜘蛛眼来喂食一只沙漠蛛蜂并驯服它

items.en: Create a Mysterious Worm by putting a Crimson Mosquito Larva in a Capsid.
items.zh: 将一只绯红蚊子幼虫放进衣壳中来创造出一种神秘的蠕虫。

items.en: Toss the Mysterious Worm into the void of the End, and prepare to meet the Void Worm.
items.zh: 把神秘的蠕虫丢进末地的虚空里来准备迎接虚空蠕虫吧。

items.en: Split a void worm in half by attacking one of its body segments. More worms, more problems!
items.zh: 攻击虚空蠕虫的身体使其一分为二，更多蠕虫，更多麻烦！

items.en: Using the drops of the Void Worm, create the Dimensional Carver, which allows you to dig through the fabric of reality to return home at any given point.
items.zh: 利用虚空蠕虫的掉落物，来制作一把允许你在真实世界的脉络中进行穿越，并可以在任何地方返回定点的维度撕裂者。

items.en: Have food stolen from your inventory by a seagull.
items.zh: 让海鸥偷走你的物品栏里的食物。

Craft a Knife to scavenge extra goods from plants and animals
items.zh: 合成一把刀来从植物和动物上获取更多资源！

items.en: Harvest grass, wheat or rice with a Knife to collect Straw
items.zh: 使用刀割下长草的植物以获取一些草秆

items.en: Place down some Organic Compost. It composts better with sun, water and mushrooms!
items.zh: 放置一些有机肥料。要是有阳光、水和蘑菇就更好了!

items.en: Organic Compost slowly decays into Rich Soil, an upgrade for your farms!
items.zh: 放置有机肥料，让它分解直到变成沃土。菌落能加速这一过程！

items.en: Use a Knife to extract Ham from Pigs or Hoglins
items.zh: 刀可以更精准仔细地切开动物的肉。刀劈有时候能产出更大的肉块！

items.en: With a tool in hand, use a Cutting Board to break down an item
items.zh: 工具到手，在砧板上切开一些东西

items.en: If You Can't Take the Heat...
Spend a whole Netherite Ingot to upgrade your knife! Or get out of the kitchen.
items.zh: 要么在你的刀上花一整块下界合金锭，要么离开厨房

items.en: Four new crops may be found in the wild, across many climates... or maybe in a chest somewhere.
items.zh: 有四种新的作物在野外等待着你，你需要跨越山和大海……或者只需要翻翻箱子。

items.en: With an overlay on, you'll see two new hotbars for attacks and abilities available to you in this mode. While holding %s or %s, your 1-9 keys and mouse wheel can be used to choose an attack or ability respectively. Empty slots are for attacks/abilities which you haven't yet unlocked and therefore are skipped over.
items.zh: 打开UI面板后, 您会看到在此面板下左上角会出现两个新快捷栏，分别是攻击和能力。按住%s或%s键时，您的1-9键和鼠标滚轮可用于分别切换攻击和能力释放方式。空槽是您尚未解锁的攻击/能力，因此会被跳过。

items.en: You can perform the attack you have selected by pressing %1$s. Similarly, to use the selected ability, press %2$s. Performing an attack/ability will (in most cases) cancel vanilla attack/interaction.
items.zh: 您可以按下%1$s键帮助你切换攻击方式。同理，如果您可以通过按下%2$s切换能力，使用攻击/能力将（在大多数情况下）取消攻击/能力。

items.en: If you have a summonable Stand, press %s to summon/unsummon it. If the Stand you have summoned can be controlled manually (i.e. most of the Stands which take form of an entity), pressing %s will switch between normal mode and manual control mode, in which you can directly control your Stand's movements.

items.en: In JJBA, Hamon is a form of energy produced by trained fighters via breathing. This energy has properties similar to sunlight's, making it fatal to zombies, vampires, and Pillar Men. In this mod it is one of the unique powers you can get.
items.zh: 在JOJO中，波纹是训练有素的战士通过呼吸产生的一种能量，这种能量是太阳的能量，对僵尸、吸血鬼和柱之男来说是致命的，在此模组中，它是你可以获得的特殊能力之一

items.en: To use Hamon effectively, you have to manage your breath, represented by %s in the left upper corner.
items.zh: 要更有效率的使用波纹，你必须规律地控制你的呼吸，以左上角的 %s 表示

items.en: All the Hamon moves, like Overdrive, Healing, or any other ones you unlock, spend %s.
items.zh: 所有波纹能力，例如波纹疾走、治疗或你解锁的任何其他能力，都会消耗%s

items.en: Hamon energy is filled by using the special %s, bound to Middle Mouse Button by default.
items.zh: 波纹能量可以通过使用专门的 %s 来补充，默认情况下绑定在鼠标中键

items.en: The translucent part of the bar is referred to as %s. If you do not refill Hamon energy, breath stability is used up instead. Spending it makes your Hamon weaker and lowers the energy cap for a little while.
items.zh: %s条显示为能量条中的半透明部分，如果不补充波纹能量，呼吸稳定将会被耗尽， 消耗它使用的波纹技能将会变弱，并一段时间内降低能量上限

items.en: If you manage your Hamon energy well, you will not have to worry about that.
items.zh: 如果你能合理地掌握呼吸，你就不必担心这个问题

items.en: With proper training you can become a stronger Hamon warrior. The next tab shows your Hamon stats and explains the training process.
items.zh: 通过适当的训练，你可以成为更强大的波纹战士。 下面一个选项卡可以显示你的波纹统计数据，并解释训练过程

items.en: Use Hamon Breath to breathe through the mask
items.zh: 请通过使用呼吸法纠正面具进行波纹呼吸

items.en: Determines the power of your Hamon attacks. Is trained by using Hamon attacks.
items.zh: 决定你波纹造成的波纹伤害，使用波纹进行攻击以锻炼你的波纹力量

items.en: Determines the amount of Hamon energy spent and efficiency of your Hamon abilities. Is trained by using Hamon abilities.
items.zh: 决定你波纹能力所消耗的能量，使用波纹能力以锻炼你的波纹控制

items.en: The level won't increase unless you increase your breathing training level
items.zh: 你必须提高呼吸技巧等级，否则该项等级不会提高

items.en: This stat increases your breathing ability as well as your physical condition.
items.zh: 它能提高你的呼吸能力和身体状况。

items.en: You'll need to constantly train it in order to make progress in learning Hamon.
items.zh: 为了在学习波纹的过程中取得进步，你需要不断地训练该数据。

items.en: To train your breathing, you have to complete these exercises daily. Complete at least 3 of them each day for maximum results. It is also recommended to craft and wear a %s if you want to commit to your Hamon training.
items.zh: 要训练的话，你必须每天完成这些练习任务，每天至少完成其中的三项或者四项，才能获得最大的效率，建议在波纹训练的早期阶段制作并佩戴%s。

items.en: The training level will slowly decrease if you stop doing the exercises!
items.zh: 如果停止练习，波纹水平就会慢慢下降，除非你的波纹呼吸水平达到100级！

items.en: You won't be able to increase your Hamon Strength/Hamon Control %s or more levels above the breathing training level.
items.zh: 你无法将你的波纹力量/波纹控制提升到%s或更高的等级以上。

items.zh: 你可以学习一项新能力！

items.zh: 你无法学习新的天赋能力!

items.zh: 你已达到天赋能力的满级！

items.zh: 你不能学习其他的天赋能力（如果你出于某种原因看到了这一个消息，这意味着这个屏幕正被偷看）

items.en: You can only learn this from another Hamon user
items.zh: 你只能从波纹大师那里学习波纹!

items.en: No one nearby you has learned this skill
items.zh: 你附近没人学过这项能力!

items.en: The most basic application of Hamon. The user channels the Hamon energy through their fist, and deals damage either with a direct punch, or by transmitting the energy through a solid or liquid material.
items.zh: 波纹最基本的应用，使用者通过拳头传导波纹能量，并直接通过拳击，固体和液体传导能量来造成伤害

items.en: Various materials can be imbued with Hamon energy. Living organisms can retain the energy for a longer time.
items.zh: 各种东西都可以灌注波纹能量，生物可以更长时间地保留能量。

items.en: Hamon can help its user exceed the limits of their movement capabilities and attack range.
items.zh: 波纹能量可以帮助其使用者激发身体潜能，增强他们的速度和攻击范围

items.en: Hamon energy can speed up the regeneration of a living body.
items.zh: 波纹能量蕴含着生命能量

items.en: Attractant and repellent Hamon are two opposite types of Hamon energy, each having their special use cases.
items.zh: 吸引型波纹和排斥型波纹是两种相反类型的波纹能量，每种都有其特殊的用法

items.en: Hamon energy can affect organisms by vibrating the water inside their bodies.
items.zh: 波纹呼吸法与肉体息息相关，合理运用或许能有奇效

items.en: The user's unarmed punches deal additional Hamon damage. Hamon is especially effective against undead creatures.
items.zh: 玩家空手时的拳击会造成额外的波纹伤害，对不死生物效果拔群！

items.en: Shift variation - Hamon Beat - is a stronger attack with extra knockback.
Applying this attack to a wall or floor creates a wave of Hamon energy, which damages mobs and players in the area.
items.zh: 向墙壁或地面施加波纹，产生波纹能量波对周围生物造成伤害

items.en: While underwater, the user can transfer a powerful wave of Hamon energy through water.
items.zh: 在水下时，玩家可以释放出强大的波纹能量

items.en: A Hamon-charged heavy blow. By charging the attack for longer, the user can channel more Hamon energy into the punch to deal a lot of damage.
Snowballs, eggs and splash water bottles the user throws inflict additional Hamon damage.
items.zh: 玩家投掷的雪球、鸡蛋和水瓶等投掷物将会附有波纹并造成伤害

items.en: The user temporarily charges a block of a plant with Hamon. While it's charged, mobs and players will take Hamon damage upon touching it.
items.zh: 玩家用波纹向方块灌注波纹。生物和玩家会在触碰它时受到波纹伤害

items.en: Allows the user to charge living mobs and players with Hamon.
items.zh: 允许玩家向生物和海龟蛋灌注波纹

items.en: When throwing out a plant, the user charges it with Hamon. Mobs and players getting too close to it will take Hamon damage.
items.zh: 当扔出植物类物品时，玩家将会向其灌注波纹，靠近它的生物将会受到伤害

items.en: Arrows and tridents the user shoots inflict additional Hamon damage.
items.zh: 玩家发射出的箭矢和三叉戟会造成额外的波纹伤害

items.en: Extends the user's arm, allowing them to punch an enemy from longer distance, additionally dealing Hamon damage.
items.zh: 让胳膊的关节脱臼来延长攻击距离的基础攻击招式，脱臼时的疼痛会被波纹所缓解

items.en: Allows the user to leap forward by jumping while sneaking.
items.zh: 允许玩家在潜行时按下跳跃键向前飞跃

items.en: Gives the user Speed and Haste effects for a short amount of time.
items.zh: 短时间使用波纹激发玩家的身体机能，为玩家提供速度和急迫效果

items.en: Speed Boost ability gives stronger effects. Leap's strength is increased. Maximum speed boost summons the user's afterimages.
items.zh: 身体加速控制将提供更强的加速效果并使玩家产生残影;飞跃的效果增强
通过使用波纹对玩家进行治疗，让玩家缓慢恢复血量

items.en: Allows the user to heal others with Healing ability while sneaking.
items.zh: （shift+对准目标长按治疗）允许玩家通过波纹的治疗能力治疗他人

items.en: The Healing ability can apply bone meal effect.
items.zh: 治疗能力对植物使用可以起到类似于骨粉的作用.

items.en: The user's Healing ability also removes Poison, Hunger, Wither and Nausea effects.
items.zh: 玩家的治疗能力将可以帮助目标排出体内的毒素（治疗时持续减少剧毒，饥饿，凋零和反胃效果的持续时间）

items.en: Lets the user adhere to a vertical surface and climb it.
items.zh: 允许玩家使用波纹依附在方块表面上攀爬它

items.en: Allows the user to freely walk on a liquid surface. Press double Shift to disable.
items.zh: 允许玩家在液体表面行走，双击Shift将会停止使用。

items.en: Turns a block of leaves into a hang glider. If not continuously charged with Hamon energy, the glider will disintegrate.
items.zh: 将一块树叶变成滑翔伞；如果不持续对树叶充能波纹，那么滑翔伞就会解体

items.en: Creates a projectile reflecting barrier in front of the user.
items.zh: 创建一个防护壁，可以反弹任何的投掷物

items.en: Creates a Hamon-charged coating on the surface of the user's body, reducing the incoming physical damage.
items.zh: 在身体表面形成一层排斥波纹，对来袭的物体产生排斥并降低受到的物理伤害

items.en: Gives entities around the user Glowing effect.
items.zh: 使用波纹的力量来感应周围的生物

items.en: The user temporarily tames a tameable animal.
items.zh: 允许玩家临时驯服一只可驯服的生物

items.en: The user applies a Hamon charge directly to a living creature's head, incapacitating them for a short time. The shock wears off if the target takes damage.
items.zh: 向生物头部施加波纹，使其短时间失去行动能力。 The shock wears off if the target takes damage.

items.en: Whenever the user attack an undead with Hamon, it continues spreading through the target's body, weakening it and slowing down its regeneration.
items.zh: 当玩家用波纹攻击亡灵生物时，它就会持续在对方的身体中扩散，造成额外的伤害

items.en: Choosing this technique will also increase the efficiency of the following skills:
Choose carefully! You won't be able to change your technique unless you fully abandon the Hamon training and start over.
Please note that some of the skills are undergoing a rework.

items.zh: 你的波纹训练效率翻倍

items.en: A special type of Sunlight Yellow Overdrive attack that sets the target on fire.
You can perform Overdrive attack with a weapon or a tool.\nWithout a weapon, the regular Overdrive deals more damage to targets with armor or an equipped melee weapon.
items.zh: 你可以在武器和工具上缠绕波纹进行攻击，可造成额外的波纹伤害。\n在没有武器的情况下,可以通过敌人的盔甲或手持道具传导波纹能量,造成更高的伤害。

items.en: You unleash a barrage of rapid Overdrive attacks.
items.zh: 你可以运用附着波纹的双手快速攻击敌方

items.en: A more powerful variation of Overdrive Barrage, followed by a devastating finishing punch. Takes a few seconds to charge.
Infuse a bottle of liquid with Hamon and shoot the liquid out at high speed. In addition to Hamon damage, the potion's effect is applied to the target.
items.zh: 在药水中灌注波纹，然后高速投掷灌注波纹的药水。除了波纹伤害外，药水的效果也会施加到目标身上

items.en: You charge forward, hitting all enemies on your way with your knee, additionally dealing Hamon damage to them.
items.zh: 向前冲锋，并使用膝盖攻击冲锋过程中的所有敌人，并对他们造成额外的波纹伤害

items.en: By spinning at high speed, you deal Hamon damage to the enemies around you. This attack is especially deadly while falling.
items.zh: 通过高速旋转，你可以对周围的敌人造成波纹伤害。这种攻击在下坠时使用对敌人尤其致命

items.en: When you die, you transfer all of your life energy (Hamon Strength and Control levels) to a nearby Hamon User.
items.zh: 当你死亡时，你会将所有生命能量（波纹力量和波纹控制）转移给附近的一名波纹使者

items.en: Allows you to use a pair of clackers as a Hamon-infused melee weapon or charge and throw it at the opponent at high speed.
items.zh: 允许你使用一对钢珠旋风作为灌注波纹的远程/近战武器，并可以高速的向对手投掷

items.en: Right-clicking a string temporarily turns connected strings into a Hamon-charged cobweb. While sneaking, you automatically place a string from your hotbar.
items.zh: 右键单击线会暂时将连接的线转换为持续缠绕着波纹的线网。在潜行时，你会自动将一根线放到地面上

items.en: When you are about to die, you will avoid death and gain Invisibility effect (once an in-game day).\nYour next words: \
items.zh: 当你即将被杀死时，你会规避死亡并获得短暂隐形效果（在游戏中每一天都会拥有一次规避死亡的机会，无法叠加）。\n你的下一句话是: \

items.en: You get into a defensive stance and swing with both elbows. If attacked in melee during a specific timing window, your strike parries the attack, dealing devastating amount of Hamon damage and extra knockback.
items.zh: 使用双肘进行防御并对前方目标造成少量波纹伤害，如果这段期间被近战攻击命中将会减免该次伤害并对目标造成大量波纹伤害

items.en: All bubble attacks consume soap, which comes in form of Soap Solution bottles, or Soap Coated Gloves.
items.zh: 所有有关泡泡的攻击都需要使用泡泡水手套才能触发

items.en: Shoot a barrage of Hamon-charged bubbles.
Shoot out disc-shaped bubbles, which move at a high velocity. Gliding variation bubbles are more precise and, instead of hitting the ground, continue to glide above it.
items.zh: 发射出圆盘状的泡沫，这些泡沫以高速移动。滑动泡沫更精准，如果泡沫撞击到地面的话，他不会破碎，取而代之的是继续在地面上滑动

items.en: Shoot a large-sized bubble, which traps its target for a few seconds.
items.zh: 你可以发射出一个巨大的泡泡，将目标困住几秒钟

items.en: When you die, you put your life energy (Hamon Strength and Control levels) into a bubble, from which it can be transferred to another Hamon user.
items.zh: 当你死亡时，你将你的生命能量（波纹力量和波纹控制）放入一个血泡泡中，它可以转移给附近的一名波纹使者

items.en: You can instantly charge an Aja Stone with Hamon. When using a regular Aja Stone, you have a small chance to turn it into Super Aja.
items.zh: 你可以使用波纹来为艾哲红石充能;当使用普通的艾哲红石时，你有几率使它成为超级艾哲红石。

items.en: You get a scarf which, when worn, reduces Hamon energy spent and absorbs Hamon damage. You can use it as a Hamon-conductive melee weapon or swing it to cover a larger area of targets.
items.zh: 你会得到一条围巾，当戴上它时，可以减少使用波纹的能量消耗，并吸收波纹的伤害。你可以把它用作类似传导波纹的近战武器，可以挥舞它来进行更大范围的攻击。

items.en: When getting attacked while wearing the scarf, you jump over the attacker using the scarf and deal Hamon damage to them (has a cooldown). Attacking with the scarf while sneaking ensnares the target.
items.zh: 当你戴着围巾受到攻击时，你会用围巾跳过攻击者，对他们造成伤害（有冷却，会攻击对你进行攻击的生物并会进行发光标记）。
接下来，你下一句话一定会说 \

  "advancements.alexsmobs.crocodile.desc": "Encounter a Crocodile",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.crocodile_chestplate.title": "Cover me with... scutes?",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.crocodile_chestplate.desc": "Craft a crocodile chestplate from many crocodile scutes",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_mantis_shrimp.title": "Shrimp Friend",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_mantis_shrimp.desc": "Tame a Mantis Shrimp with many feedings of Tropical Fish",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.breed_crocodile.title": "Crikey!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.breed_crocodile.desc": "Breed two crocodiles with rotten flesh. Careful not to trample their eggs!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.alligator_snapping_turtle.title": "Alligator In Name Only",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.alligator_snapping_turtle.desc": "Encounter an Alligator Snapping Turtle",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.spiked_scute.title": "Shear the Scute",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.spiked_scute.desc": "Shear a moss-covered Alligator Snapping Turtle and obtain a Spiked Scute",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.spiked_turtle_shell.title": "Turtle-ology Majors Be Like",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.spiked_turtle_shell.desc": "Craft a Spiked Turtle Shell",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.mantis_shrimp_bucket.title": "A Fistful of Water",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.mantis_shrimp_bucket.desc": "Sneak and give a tamed Mantis Shrimp a bucket of water so that it can live on land indefinitely",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.orcas_might.title": "Free Willy",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.orcas_might.desc": "Be granted a blessing from a wild Orca",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.acacia_blossom.title": "Flowers of the Savanna",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.acacia_blossom.desc": "Obtain an Acacia Blossom from breaking Acacia Leaves",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_elephant.title": "Stampy!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_elephant.desc": "Tame an elephant by feeding it Acacia Blossoms",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_elephant_tusked.title": "The Biggest Land Mammal",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_elephant_tusked.desc": "Tame a tusked elephant when it is a baby",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.elephant_swag.title": "Dressed to Impress",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.elephant_swag.desc": "Place a colored carpet on an elephant",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.soul_vulture.title": "Fetch Me Their Souls!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.soul_vulture.desc": "Encounter a Soul Vulture in the nether",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.soul_heart.title": "The Soul-ly Ghost",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.soul_heart.desc": "Obtain a soul heart from slaying a bloated Soul Vulture",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.spectre.title": "The Iron Curtain",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.spectre.desc": "Lure a Spectre in the end with a Soul Heart. Use a lead on them to hitch a ride!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.guster.title": "Eye of The Storm",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.guster.desc": "Encounter a Guster during a stormy day in the desert",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.gustmaker.title": "I Am Become Guster",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.gustmaker.desc": "Craft a Gustmaker. Now you can make your own mini-storms!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.pocket_sand.title": "Pocket Sand!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.pocket_sand.desc": "Craft a Pocket Of Sand. Sha-sha!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.crimson_mosquito_sick.title": "Down with the Sickness",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.crimson_mosquito_sick.desc": "Feed a Crimson Mosquito a strange, fungal creature covered in Warped Fungus. Watch as the Crimson Mosquito transforms!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.warped_mosco_kill.title": "Destroyer of Chads",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.warped_mosco_kill.desc": "Slay the Warped Mosco, the swole defender of the Warped Forest.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.hemolymph_blaster.title": "Blast from the... Future?",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.hemolymph_blaster.desc": "Craft a Hemolyph Blaster, the ultimate upgrade to the Blood Sprayer.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.straddler.title": "Straddle My Ol' Saddle",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.straddler.desc": "Encounter a Straddler in the Basalt Deltas.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.stradpole_feed.title": "Like Father",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.stradpole_feed.desc": "Feed a Stradpole some Mosquito Larva, in hopes of turning it into a Straddler.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.straddleboard.title": "Surf Wax America",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.straddleboard.desc": "Craft a Straddleboard from some Netherite and Straddlerite.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.emu.title": "It's an Emu!!!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.emu.desc": "Encounter an Emu. Exercise caution.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.emu_dodge.title": "Begun, The Emu War Has",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.emu_dodge.desc": "See an emu dodge a launched projectile.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.kangaroo.title": "We do a little trolling...",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.kangaroo.desc": "Encounter a Kangaroo",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.save_cachalot_whale.title": "Save the Whales!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.save_cachalot_whale.desc": "Save a beached Cachalot Whale by pushing it into the water, and then have it reward you by coughing up some Ambergris",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.echolocator.title": "Echo-muh-cation!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.echolocator.desc": "Craft an Echolocator, which can reveal nearby caves",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.endolocator.title": "No End In Signt",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.endolocator.desc": "Craft an Endolocator, which can reveal nearby End Portal Frames",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.stomp_leafcutter_anthill.title": "Ant-Agonizer",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.stomp_leafcutter_anthill.desc": "Stomp on a Leafcutter Anthill - beware the angry denizens within!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.gongylidia.title": "Like a Truffle, with more Ant",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.gongylidia.desc": "Harvest Gongylidia from a Leafcutter Ant Chamber underground. Place Shroomlight near the chamber to make sure you don't upset the locals",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.leafcutter_ant_pupa.title": "Ant Farm",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.leafcutter_ant_pupa.desc": "Obtain a Leafcutter Ant Pupa, which can be placed on dirt to start a Leafcutter Ant colony.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.enderiophage.title": "Ender Distancing",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.enderiophage.desc": "Encounter an Enderiophage, a giant biomechanical construct found in the End Midlands. Be careful not to catch Ender Flu!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.capsid.title": "Capsid-19",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.capsid.desc": "Obtain a Capsid from a slain Enderiophage. Use it to display items or to transfer them upwards",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.ender_flu.title": "Race Against The Clock",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.ender_flu.desc": "Catch the Ender Flu effect. Cure it by eating many Chorus Fruit or drinking milk. Be sure not to let it run its toll!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.enderiophage_rocket.title": "Ad End-stra",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.enderiophage_rocket.desc": "Craft an Enderiophage Rocket, which can be used in place of Firework Rockets when in the End.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_bald_eagle.title": "Freedom Intensifies",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_bald_eagle.desc": "Tame a bald eagle with fish oil.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.falconry_glove.title": "Hand In Glove",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.falconry_glove.desc": "Craft a Falconry Glove from Leather and Hair of Bear. Use it to pick up and launch tamed eagles!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.falconry_hood.title": "Blindsided",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.falconry_hood.desc": "Craft a Falconry Hood from Leather and a Roadrunner Feather. Eagles wearing one can be manually directed!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.bald_eagle_challenge.title": "Winning Play",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.bald_eagle_challenge.desc": "Kill any creature from 100 blocks away with an eagle wearing a hood.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tigers_blessing.title": "Eye of the Tiger",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tigers_blessing.desc": "Receive a Tiger's Blessing after feeding it Porkchops, Chicken or other meats.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tarantula_hawk.title": "Rigged from the Start",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tarantula_hawk.desc": "Encounter a Tarantula Hawk in a desert.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_tarantula_hawk.title": "Big Iron",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.tame_tarantula_hawk.desc": "Tame a Tarantula Hawk by feeding it Spider Eyes.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.mysterious_worm.title": "Destroy The Child",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.mysterious_worm.desc": "Create a Mysterious Worm by putting a Crimson Mosquito Larva in a Capsid.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.void_worm_summon.title": "A Soul for a Soul",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.void_worm_summon.desc": "Toss the Mysterious Worm into the void of the End, and prepare to meet the Void Worm.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.void_worm_split.title": "Should've Gone for the Head",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.void_worm_split.desc": "Split a void worm in half by attacking one of its body segments. More worms, more problems!",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.void_worm_kill.title": "Wormy",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.void_worm_kill.desc": "Destroy the End Worm.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.dimensional_carver.title": "Break On Through...",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.dimensional_carver.desc": "Using the drops of the Void Worm, create the Dimensional Carver, which allows you to dig through the fabric of reality to return home at any given point.",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.seagull_steal.title": "Mine? Mine? Mine?",
  "advancements.alexsmobs.seagull_steal.desc": "Have food stolen from your inventory by a seagull."
}

  "hamon.intro.tab": "Introduction",
  "hamon.intro.about.name": "About Hamon",
  "hamon.intro.about.text": "In JJBA, Hamon is a form of energy produced by trained fighters via breathing. This energy has properties similar to sunlight's, making it fatal to zombies, vampires, and Pillar Men. In this mod it is one of the unique powers you can get.",

  "hamon.intro.breath.text1": "To use Hamon effectively, you have to manage your breath, represented by %s in the left upper corner.",

  "hamon.intro.breath.text2": "All the Hamon moves, like Overdrive, Healing, or any other ones you unlock, spend %s.",

  "hamon.intro.breath.text3": "Hamon energy is filled by using the special %s, bound to Middle Mouse Button by default.",

  "hamon.intro.breath.text5": "If you manage your Hamon energy well, you will not have to worry about that.",

  "hamon.skills.overdrive.desc": "The most basic application of Hamon. The user channels the Hamon energy through their fist, and deals damage either with a direct punch, or by transmitting the energy through a solid or liquid material.",
  "hamon.skills.infusion.desc": "Various materials can be imbued with Hamon energy. Living organisms can retain the energy for a longer time.",
  "hamon.skills.flexibility.desc": "Hamon can help its user exceed the limits of their movement capabilities and attack range.",
  "hamon.skills.life.desc": "Hamon energy can speed up the regeneration of a living body.",
  "hamon.skills.attractant_repellent.desc": "Attractant and repellent Hamon are two opposite types of Hamon energy, each having their special use cases.",
  "hamon.skills.body_manipulation.desc": "Hamon energy can affect organisms by vibrating the water inside their bodies.",

  "hamonSkill.overdrive.name": "Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.overdrive.desc": "The user's unarmed punches deal additional Hamon damage. Hamon is especially effective against undead creatures.",
  "hamonSkill.overdrive_strong.desc": "Shift variation - Hamon Beat - is a stronger attack with extra knockback.",
  "hamonSkill.sendo_overdrive.name": "Sendo Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.sendo_overdrive.desc": "Applying this attack to a wall or floor creates a wave of Hamon energy, which damages mobs and players in the area.",
  "hamonSkill.turquoise_blue_overdrive.name": "Turquoise Blue Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.turquoise_blue_overdrive.desc": "While underwater, the user can transfer a powerful wave of Hamon energy through water.",
  "hamonSkill.sunlight_yellow_overdrive.name": "Sunlight Yellow Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.sunlight_yellow_overdrive.desc": "A Hamon-charged heavy blow. By charging the attack for longer, the user can channel more Hamon energy into the punch to deal a lot of damage.",
  "hamonSkill.throwables_infusion.name": "Throwables Infusion",
  "hamonSkill.throwables_infusion.desc": "Snowballs, eggs and splash water bottles the user throws inflict additional Hamon damage.",
  "hamonSkill.plant_infusion.name": "Plants Infusion (block)",
  "hamonSkill.plant_infusion.desc": "The user temporarily charges a block of a plant with Hamon. While it's charged, mobs and players will take Hamon damage upon touching it.",
  "hamonSkill.animal_infusion.name": "Living Organism Infusion",
  "hamonSkill.animal_infusion.desc": "Allows the user to charge living mobs and players with Hamon.",
  "hamonSkill.plant_item_infusion.name": "Plants Infusion (item)",
  "hamonSkill.plant_item_infusion.desc": "When throwing out a plant, the user charges it with Hamon. Mobs and players getting too close to it will take Hamon damage.",
  "hamonSkill.arrow_infusion.name": "Arrow Infusion",
  "hamonSkill.arrow_infusion.desc": "Arrows and tridents the user shoots inflict additional Hamon damage.",
  "hamonSkill.zoom_punch.name": "Zoom Punch",
  "hamonSkill.zoom_punch.desc": "Extends the user's arm, allowing them to punch an enemy from longer distance, additionally dealing Hamon damage.",
  "hamonSkill.jump.name": "Leap",
  "hamonSkill.jump.desc": "Allows the user to leap forward by jumping while sneaking.",
  "hamonSkill.speed_boost.name": "Speed Boost",
  "hamonSkill.speed_boost.desc": "Gives the user Speed and Haste effects for a short amount of time.",
  "hamonSkill.afterimages.name": "Body Control Mastery (WIP)",
  "hamonSkill.afterimages.desc": "Speed Boost ability gives stronger effects. Leap's strength is increased. Maximum speed boost summons the user's afterimages. ",
  "hamonSkill.healing.name": "Healing",
  "hamonSkill.healing.desc": "Gives the user Regeneration effect.",
  "hamonSkill.healing_touch.name": "Healing Touch",
  "hamonSkill.healing_touch.desc": "Allows the user to heal others with Healing ability while sneaking.",
  "hamonSkill.plants_growth.name": "Plants Growth",
  "hamonSkill.plants_growth.desc": "The Healing ability can apply bone meal effect.",
  "hamonSkill.expel_venom.name": "Expel Venom",
  "hamonSkill.expel_venom.desc": "The user's Healing ability also removes Poison, Hunger, Wither and Nausea effects.",
  "hamonSkill.wall_climbing.name": "Wall Climbing",
  "hamonSkill.wall_climbing.desc": "Lets the user adhere to a vertical surface and climb it.",
  "hamonSkill.liquid_walking.name": "Liquid Walking",
  "hamonSkill.liquid_walking.desc": "Allows the user to freely walk on a liquid surface. Press double Shift to disable.",
  "hamonSkill.life_magnetism.name": "Life Magnetism",
  "hamonSkill.life_magnetism.desc": "Turns a block of leaves into a hang glider. If not continuously charged with Hamon energy, the glider will disintegrate.",
  "hamonSkill.projectile_shield.name": "Projectile Barrier",
  "hamonSkill.projectile_shield.desc": "Creates a projectile reflecting barrier in front of the user.",
  "hamonSkill.protection.name": "Repelling Hamon",
  "hamonSkill.protection.desc": "Creates a Hamon-charged coating on the surface of the user's body, reducing the incoming physical damage.",
  "hamonSkill.detector.name": "Detector",
  "hamonSkill.detector.desc": "Gives entities around the user Glowing effect.",
  "hamonSkill.hypnosis.name": "Animal Hypnosis",
  "hamonSkill.hypnosis.desc": "The user temporarily tames a tameable animal.",
  "hamonSkill.hamon_shock.name": "Hamon Shock",
  "hamonSkill.hamon_shock.desc": "The user applies a Hamon charge directly to a living creature's head, incapacitating them for a short time. The shock wears off if the target takes damage.",
  "hamonSkill.hamon_spread.name": "Hamon Spread",
  "hamonSkill.hamon_spread.desc": "Whenever the user attack an undead with Hamon, it continues spreading through the target's body, weakening it and slowing down its regeneration.",

  "hamonSkill.natural_talent.name": "Natural Talent",
  "hamonSkill.natural_talent.desc": "Your Hamon training is 2x faster.",
  "hamonSkill.scarlet_overdrive.name": "Scarlet Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.scarlet_overdrive.desc": "A special type of Sunlight Yellow Overdrive attack that sets the target on fire.",
  "hamonSkill.metal_silver_overdrive.name": "Metal Silver Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.metal_silver_overdrive.desc": "You can perform Overdrive attack with a weapon or a tool.\nWithout a weapon, the regular Overdrive deals more damage to targets with armor or an equipped melee weapon.",
  "hamonSkill.overdrive_barrage.name": "Overdrive Barrage",
  "hamonSkill.overdrive_barrage.desc": "You unleash a barrage of rapid Overdrive attacks.",
  "hamonSkill.syo_barrage.name": "Sunlight Yellow Overdrive Barrage (WIP)",
  "hamonSkill.syo_barrage.desc": "A more powerful variation of Overdrive Barrage, followed by a devastating finishing punch. Takes a few seconds to charge.",
  "hamonSkill.hamon_cutter.name": "Hamon Cutter",
  "hamonSkill.hamon_cutter.desc": "Infuse a bottle of liquid with Hamon and shoot the liquid out at high speed. In addition to Hamon damage, the potion's effect is applied to the target.",
  "hamonSkill.sendo_wave_kick.name": "Sendo Wave Kick",
  "hamonSkill.sendo_wave_kick.desc": "You charge forward, hitting all enemies on your way with your knee, additionally dealing Hamon damage to them.",
  "hamonSkill.tornado_overdrive.name": "Tornado Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.tornado_overdrive.desc": "By spinning at high speed, you deal Hamon damage to the enemies around you. This attack is especially deadly while falling.",
  "hamonSkill.deep_pass.name": "Deep Pass Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.deep_pass.desc": "When you die, you transfer all of your life energy (Hamon Strength and Control levels) to a nearby Hamon User.",
  "hamonSkill.clacker_volley.name": "Clacker Volley (WIP)",
  "hamonSkill.clacker_volley.desc": "Allows you to use a pair of clackers as a Hamon-infused melee weapon or charge and throw it at the opponent at high speed.",
  "hamonSkill.rope_trap.name": "Rope Trap (WIP)",
  "hamonSkill.rope_trap.desc": "Right-clicking a string temporarily turns connected strings into a Hamon-charged cobweb. While sneaking, you automatically place a string from your hotbar.",
  "hamonSkill.cheat_death.name": "Cheat Death",
  "hamonSkill.cheat_death.desc": "When you are about to die, you will avoid death and gain Invisibility effect (once an in-game day).\nYour next words: \"What does it have to do with Hamon?\"",
  "hamonSkill.rebuff_overdrive.name": "Rebuff Overdrive",
  "hamonSkill.rebuff_overdrive.desc": "You get into a defensive stance and swing with both elbows. If attacked in melee during a specific timing window, your strike parries the attack, dealing devastating amount of Hamon damage and extra knockback.",
  "hamon.caesar_soap_hint.name": "Resource: Soap",
  "hamon.caesar_soap_hint.desc": "All bubble attacks consume soap, which comes in form of Soap Solution bottles, or Soap Coated Gloves.",
  "hamonSkill.bubble_launcher.name": "Bubble Launcher",
  "hamonSkill.bubble_launcher.desc": "Shoot a barrage of Hamon-charged bubbles.",
  "hamonSkill.bubble_cutter.name": "Bubble Cutter",
  "hamonSkill.bubble_cutter.desc": "Shoot out disc-shaped bubbles, which move at a high velocity. Gliding variation bubbles are more precise and, instead of hitting the ground, continue to glide above it.",
  "hamonSkill.bubble_barrier.name": "Bubble Barrier",
  "hamonSkill.bubble_barrier.desc": "Shoot a large-sized bubble, which traps its target for a few seconds.",
  "hamonSkill.crimson_bubble.name": "Crimson Bubble",
  "hamonSkill.crimson_bubble.desc": "When you die, you put your life energy (Hamon Strength and Control levels) into a bubble, from which it can be transferred to another Hamon user.",
  "hamonSkill.aja_stone_keeper.name": "Keeper of Aja Stone",
  "hamonSkill.aja_stone_keeper.desc": "You can instantly charge an Aja Stone with Hamon. When using a regular Aja Stone, you have a small chance to turn it into Super Aja.",
  "hamonSkill.satiporoja_scarf.name": "Satiporoja Beetle Scarf (WIP)",
  "hamonSkill.satiporoja_scarf.desc": "You get a scarf which, when worn, reduces Hamon energy spent and absorbs Hamon damage. You can use it as a Hamon-conductive melee weapon or swing it to cover a larger area of targets.",
  "hamonSkill.snake_muffler.name": "Snake Muffler (WIP)",
  "hamonSkill.snake_muffler.desc": "When getting attacked while wearing the scarf, you jump over the attacker using the scarf and deal Hamon damage to them (has a cooldown). Attacking with the scarf while sneaking ensnares the target.",

  "item.tetra.scroll.warforge.details": "§l§nWarforging§r\n\nWarforging a double headed tool makes it much more effective in combat, this provides:\n\n + a §lpassive§r stat or effect based on the warforged head\n\n + a right-click §lability§r based on the left head\n\n + an ability §lmodifier§r based on the right head\r§l§nBattleaxes§r\n\n§lPassive:§r Severing\nAttacks have a chance to reduce the target's max health\n\n§lAbility:§r Execute\nDeals bonus damage based on missing health and harmful effects\n\n§lModifier:§r Overcharge\nAbilities can be charged up further to increase damage and improve effects\r§l§nWarhammers§r\n\n§lPassive:§r Crushing\nAttacks partially bypass armor and absorption effects\n\n§lAbility:§r Slam\nAttack a single target with a strong knockback, or hit multiple enemies in a large area\n\n§lModifier:§r Momentum\nCauses abilities to stun targets or knock them back further\r§l§nWar-picks§r\n\n§lPassive:§r Skewering\nAttacks deal bonus damage to unarmored targets\n\n§lAbility:§r Puncture\nReduces the target's armor or cause them to bleed\n\n§lModifier:§r Combo\nGain combo points from regular attacks which improves abilities\r§l§nTool butts§r\n\n§lPassive:§r Light\nProvides a significant speed increase but reduces the tier of the tool\n\n§lAbility:§r None\n\n§lModifier:§r Light\nReduces ability charge time and cooldown\r§l§nClaws§r\n\n§lPassive:§r Armor pen.\nAttacks partially ignore armor\n\n§lAbility:§r Pry\nApplies a stacking armor reduction effect on the target\n\n§lModifier:§r Revenge\nImproves abilities when the wielder is at a disadvantage\r§l§nGuisarmes (hoes)§r\n\n§lPassive:§r Damage bonus\nIncreases overall weapon damage\n\n§lAbility:§r Overpower\nDeals high damage but exhausts both the target and the wielder\n\n§lModifier:§r Overextend\nAbilities are more effective but drains additional food\r§l§nWarsickles§r\n\n§lPassive:§r Sweeping\nIncreased sweep damage and range\n\n§lAbility:§r Reap\nHits targets in an area, kills empower the wielder\n\n§lModifier:§r Exhilaration\nEmpowers abilities when used successfully\r§l§nBattleadzes§r\n\n§lPassive:§r Damage bonus\nSignificantly increases damage for the adze head\n\n§lAbility:§r Lunge\nLunge forward and deal damage to the first target hit\n\n§lModifier:§r Defensive\nAbilities grant defensive bonuses when the item is used in the offhand",

items.en: &6『JOJOの奇妙冒险』&7(完成“觉醒！奇妙的JOJO启程”解锁)
波纹、替身、吸血鬼、柱之男
「需先完成 “觉醒！奇妙的JOJO启程” 任务」
有股神秘的力量吸引着你
靠近陨石核心的时候一定要是满血，否则...
柱子上的这个石像是谁？！
放这么久没烂，保鲜一定很好(
普通人吃下，吸血鬼吃下，效果各有不同
合成获得，材料来自阿图姆
可以使用棺材跳过白天
棺材是用来跳过白天的
呼吸会在你的身体里引出波纹
建议带着手套,这样使用技能就不用单独空手了
替身技能也可以带着手套释放
具体的训练流程可以从波纹大师处学习
按下“shift+X”可以打开波纹模式
带着石鬼面攻击村民,或者是自残
变为柱之男之后切勿使用以下能力
可以进化为和卡兹一样的柱之男
距离究极生物只有一步之遥
与石鬼面使用方式相同
在白天可以吸收阳光从而发射阳光
PS：这是一次性的，用完就爆
2.学习“莉莎莉莎”的波纹流派，并学习了“艾哲红石的守护者”技能，使用艾哲红石有极小概率获得。
3.击败凋零用下界之星与艾哲红石合成。
除了发射阳光伤害更高、不再是一次性物品以外，
还可以用来与石鬼面结合成为终极石鬼面.
使用前保证自己拥有至少30-45级经验
同时保证自己血量健康
吸血鬼受到5级虚弱（晒太阳）,再喂食一个附魔金苹果
或者注射金苹果汁注射剂
1.合成“『移除』替身(一次性)”光盘并使用
2.在村子内与“猜拳小子”猜拳,并且全输
3.联机好友用替身『白蛇』移除你的替身
&6注意:陨石碎片和艾哲红石可以在右上角商店购买
收回替身后，按X按键后，可只召唤双臂
再次按下X键关闭非完全召唤模式
把波纹力量与控制锻炼到满级
甲虫围巾对吸血鬼和波纹使者都用增益
可以减少波纹的消耗,也可以减少波纹的伤害
也是\"莉莎莉莎\"流派的技能所需要的武器
万里挑一的天赋和意志
完成全部波纹修行提升至满级
这决定了波纹恢复速度和总量上限
